00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:19,230
Akibat tipuan penyihir itu, kau akan mati.

251
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:22,039
Kau akan dicincang oleh Olivier ini!

252
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:28,500
Jangan, dia adalah...

253
00:18:28,580 --> 00:18:29,838
Aku tahu.

254
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:30,797
Dia kuat, kan.

255
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:32,280
Kita harus kabur!

256
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,425
Kenapa?

257
00:18:33,770 --> 00:18:37,763
Kalau mau benci, bencilah penyihir itu, bukan aku.

258
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:40,460
Juga bencilah dirimu yang bodoh itu!

259
00:19:21,970 --> 00:19:23,975
Apa-apaan ekspresi itu?

260
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:26,460
Kenapa kau tersenyum?

261
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:30,360
Ah, benar.

262
00:19:30,650 --> 00:19:32,150
Aku tersenyum.

263
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:36,360
Tak ada yang lebih buruk dari manusia
yang tak paham akan posisinya.

264
00:19:36,950 --> 00:19:40,680
Kamu beruntung masih bisa hidup!

265
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,970
Tidak mungkin.

266
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:02,270
Kenapa kau masih hidup?

267
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:05,010
Pertarungan tanpa dialog itu monoton.

268
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,810
Apa?

269
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:09,230
Gadis ini tak punya hati.

270
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:12,274
Dia tak menjawab pertanyaanku.

271
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:14,151
Apa kau bilang?

272
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:17,140
Cepat bunuh dia, Olivier!

273
00:20:17,150 --> 00:20:18,071
Berhenti!

274
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:18,920
Hm?

275
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:20,310
Ayo kita berhenti.

276
00:20:20,450 --> 00:20:21,200
Kenapa?

277
00:20:21,370 --> 00:20:23,827
Dia tak tertandingi oleh manusia!

278
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:26,580
Aku tak ingat, tapi aku tahu.

279
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:30,780
Bahkan untuk pemenang turnamen manusia
tak bersihir pun mustahil?

280
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:32,280
Sudahlah.

281
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:33,900
Sudah cukup.

282
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:38,250
Ingatanku sudah kembali, bahkan sudah cukup.

283
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:39,200
Hah?

284
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:41,510
Kamu tak harus mati.

285
00:20:41,670 --> 00:20:41,980
Eh?

286
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:44,200
Biar kulakukan sisanya.

287
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:44,580
Hah?

288
00:20:46,330 --> 00:20:49,640
Penyihir tanpa sihir memangnya bisa apa?

289
00:20:50,080 --> 00:20:51,940
Setidaknya meloloskan dia pergi.

290
00:20:54,020 --> 00:20:56,050
Penyihir melindungi orang lain?

291
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:58,180
Tak ada yang lebih aneh dari ini.

292
00:20:58,260 --> 00:21:01,100
Tapi kalau kau mau bekerja sama,

293
00:21:01,130 --> 00:21:03,940
maka nyawa bocah itu akan kuampuni.

294
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:05,720
Kerja sama?

295
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,380
Apa kamu bilang?

296
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,957
Dasar ingatan tak lengkap.

297
00:21:11,300 --> 00:21:13,990
Kau hanya perlu bersumpah akan bekerja sama.

298
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:16,280
Akibat kau terus menolak,

299
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:18,740
kami pun sangat-sangat terlambat.

300
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:21,180
Baiklah.

301
00:21:21,570 --> 00:21:24,880
Hei. Bisa tolong jangan mengobrol sendiri?

302
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,848
Ini semua demi dirimu!

303
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:27,960
Tidak perlu.

304
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,820
Aku dengar dari tadi.

305
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:32,860
Tapi tolong jangan anggap aku akan kalah.

306
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,606
Aku merasa tidak nyaman.

307
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:38,193
Kau tak bisa memahami situasinya?

308
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:39,960
Aku bilang kalau dia menurut,

309
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:42,130
kubiarkan dirimu lolos.

310
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,980
Kubilang tidak perlu.

311
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,140
Coba lihat.

312
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:46,580
Tunggu!

313
00:21:46,580 --> 00:21:47,630
Cukup!

314
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:49,860
Bunuh dia!

315
00:22:07,150 --> 00:22:08,740
Kau tertangkap.

